{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1506ac6726","title":"春节宴请延安附近地区劳动英雄、居民及驻军干部时的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ab9b35a9b","index":0,"year":1947,"month":1,"day":24,"articleId":"1506ac6726"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui2","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1943-1949卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui2a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a223060b89","type":"title","text":"春节宴请延安附近地区劳动英雄、居民及驻军干部时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1506ac6726"},{"id":"b15dd0b4dd","type":"paragraph","text":"积极生产、改善生活，丰衣足食，婚嫁丧葬事宜不要铺张。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1506ac6726"},{"id":"32fa6bbaf3","type":"paragraph","text":"我们好比爬山，已经快攀登到山顶，去年的困难已经克服，但对于在政治上破坏“政协”，军事上破坏“停战令”，进攻我们的蒋介石，定要坚决粉碎其进攻，争取全国和平。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1506ac6726"},{"id":"6bd9939f78","type":"paragraph","text":"军民之间，乡邻之间要和睦、团结，争取和平光景早日实现。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1506ac6726"},{"id":"d2301bbf7b","type":"paragraph","text":"（录自《解放日报》一九四七年一月二十八日）","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1506ac6726"}],"page":{"id":"8709a510c8","publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1506ac6726","start":176,"end":177}}}},"__N_SSG":true}